properties.headline: Gale Watch issued January 20 at 8:34PM CST until January 22 at 9:00PM CST by NWS Milwaukee/Sullivan WI
properties.description:
...GALES POSSIBLE OVER NORTHERN LAKE MICHIGAN STARTING TUESDAY
EVENING...

* WHAT...Southwest gales of 35 to 40 knots. Waves 8 to 12 ft
occasionally to 16 ft.

* WHERE...Northern portions of Lake Michigan.

* WHEN...From Tuesday evening through Wednesday evening.

* IMPACTS...Strong winds can cause hazardous waves which could
capsize or damage vessels and reduce visibility.
properties.instruction:
Mariners should consider altering plans to avoid possible
hazardous conditions.  Remain in port, seek safe harbor, alter
course, and/or secure the vessel for severe wind and waves.

NWSheadline: GALE WATCH IN EFFECT FROM TUESDAY EVENING THROUGH WEDNESDAY EVENING
